f:T565,Crude Palm Oil (CPO) is the world's most consumed vegetable oil, serving as feedstock for food manufacturing, oleochemicals, biodiesel, and industrial lubricants. XRT Group sources CPO directly from Malaysian and Indonesian palm mills through our Singapore hub, with RSPO Mass Balance certification available for buyers supplying EU markets under EUDR.

**Quality Specification**

Malaysian CPO: MPOB Grade A — FFA (as palmitic acid) 5% max, moisture and impurities (M&I) 0.5% max, DOBI 2.3 min. Indonesian CPO: SNI 7182:2012 equivalent. MPOB sampling and grading at origin.

**RSPO & EUDR Compliance**

XRT's oils desk maintains RSPO Mass Balance supply chain certification. Full deforestation-free documentation available under EU Deforestation Regulation (EUDR): geo-coordinates, satellite monitoring compliance, and chain-of-custody for each mill of origin.

**Logistics**

Primary loading: Port Klang and Pasir Gudang (Malaysia); Belawan and Dumai (Indonesia). Bulk liquid tanker, ISO tanks, or flexi-tanks. Singapore hub provides secondary blending and re-export.

**Applications**

Food manufacturing (frying oils, margarine, baked goods), oleochemicals, biodiesel (B7–B30), soap and personal care, industrial lubricant base.

**Pricing**

Differential to BMD FCPO front-month contract. Current indicative premium +MYR 40/MT. USD/EUR invoicing against daily BMD FX rate.8:["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12 pt-10 sm:pt-16 pb-10 sm:pb-12","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_400px] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"label-caps px-3 py-1.5 border","style":{"color":"#c8973a","borderColor":"#c8973a"},"children":"OIL-001"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"label-caps text-[#A8A5A0]","children":"Edible & Industrial Oils"}]]}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-[clamp(2.25rem,6vw,4.5rem)] text-white leading-[1.0] mb-4","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-barlow)","fontWeight":900,"letterSpacing":"-0.02em","textTransform":"uppercase"},"children":"Crude Palm Oil (CPO)"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base text-[#A8A5A0] mb-8","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-archivo)","letterSpacing":"0.04em"},"children":"FFA 5% Max / M&I 0.5%"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base sm:text-lg text-[#C4C1BE] leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-archivo)"},"children":"Crude Palm Oil from Malaysian and Indonesian mills. FFA 5% max, M&I 0.5%. BMD FCPO benchmark at +MYR 40/MT. Minimum 2,000 MT, CIF/CFR. MPOB inspection, RSPO Mass Balance and EUDR-compliant documentation. PORAM/FOSFA terms."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 border-t border-xrt-steel/15","children":[["$","div","Min. Volume",{"className":"py-5 sm:py-6 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-xrt-steel/15 sm:px-6 sm:first:pl-0","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"label-caps text-[#A8A5A0] mb-2","children":"Min. Volume"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-black text-white","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-barlow)","letterSpacing":"-0.02em"},"children":"2,000 MT"}]]}],["$",